fm: int removeDuplicates(vector<int>& nums) {     int n = nums.size();     int k = 0, i = 0;     if (n == 0) return 0;     nums[k] = nums[0];     k = k + 1;     for (i = 1; i < n; i++) {       if (nums[i] != nums[i - 1]) {         nums[k] = nums[i];         k++;       }     }     return k;   }

fm: int removeElement(vector<int>& nums, int val) {     int k = nums.size();     int beg = 0;     for (int i = 0; i < k; i++) {       if (nums[i] != val) {         nums[beg] = nums[i];         beg++;       }     }     return beg;   }
